{
  "description": "Red is super well-known as core community member on Green chain. His Giga chad badge says it more then any of my words. Been like a balm for my ears to hear his thoughts about getting Giga Chad role, that never focus on it personally, he is using all advantages on portal, like streaming, trading, gaming, collecting"
}

{
  "description": "Pavil is an incredible street artist which made a huge graffiti artworks for communities like Abstract and Pudgy Penguins, and many others.

Always supportive and have a big heart, deserves a lot of recognition for his work.

It takes a lot of effort to make something like he does, and it brings a lot of positivity and unites the space.

Also, he's done an Ironman triathlon, which takes a lot of preparation and physical health, which is so inspirational."
}

{
  "description": "Ayo, we didn't talk to much in DMs or in person. Met each other in Abstract, we both artists, both gigachads, both been on few spaces/streams. His penguins train forever in my heart lol & im sure that we will see much more art works for community from Bunya. No doubts that we will meet each other on more spaces in future & bring more attention to artists in web3, especially in Pudgy & Abstract Eco. Happy to support with review"
}

{
  "description": "Cristian leads with love and positivity. His presence makes you feel warm and welcome in any community he is a part of. I had the great pleasure of meeting him in person at NFT NYC, and that only reinforced what I felt online. He is a gifted content creator who is able to pivot seamlessly from providing thoughtful analysis to contagious laughter. I know he's someone I'll vibe with for many years to come. I've recently learned more about his expertise beyond crypto, and it only deepened my respect for him. Bonus Fact: Cristian is a pro Twerker!"
}

{"description":"I had the pleasure of meeting Becca in Dubai this year for Token 2049. She was one of the kindest and nicest people to come up to me and involve me in the activities.

I was able to connect with her on a friendly level and realize what a hard-working woman she is. She is remarkable and has made so much impact in Web3, not only through her job at AP, but also in the wider Pudgy Penguin Ecosystem.

It's been a joy to watch her live her dreams, achieve her goals, and now being part of the team."}

{"description":"AL is an incredible guy. He's always super supportive of others in the Igloo and the extended pudgy community, a well as Abstract.

I find joy watching his journey in Web3 and how he includes his family, his lifestyle creating content for his audience.

I wish there were more people like AL!"}

{
  "description": "I met N3XT through our mutual friend Elisa. N3XT is always very supportive of all of us in our friend group, he is often sharing great opportunities with all of us.\n\nHe is a kind person and great at what he does, with a lot of experience behind content and marketing."
}

{
  "description": "I’ve known Cris for a few months, and he’s been a person who constantly tries to provide value, and doesn’t participate in any drama.\n\nA great person and a businessman in what he does."
}

{
  "description": "Cristian always shows up to give his best. He is a great friend, trustworthy, always willing to recommend others to roles or projects.

Not many people know this but he's also a very successful creator in the traditional fashion industry on Instagram.

Knows a lot about marketing, would recommend him as an advisor or contractor any day"
}

{
  "description": "So grateful to have met WW through Cambria/Abstract. He's a fabulous creator and always a pleasure to talk to or play games with. He's skilled in the space but also a really great and genuine person."
}
